serverSide.objects

Class GeneralRepo

  • java.lang.Object
    • serverSide.objects.GeneralRepo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeneralRepoInterface, java.rmi.Remote

    public class GeneralRepo
extends java.lang.Object
implements GeneralRepoInterface
    General Repository. It is responsible to keep the visible the internal state of the problem and prints in the logging file. It is implemented as an implicit monitor. All public methods are executed in mutual exclusion. There are no internal synchronization points.
